Description: Wallpaper changer, downloader and manager
 Variety changes the desktop wallpaper regularly, using local or
 automatically downloaded images licensed under Creative Commons. Variety
 sits conveniently as an indicator in the panel and can be easily paused
 and resumed. The mouse wheel can be used to scroll wallpapers back and
 forth
